5 個月前\",\"text\":\"Uber Eats外送過來，麵條沒煮熟是怎樣……呈現麵糰狀態，是要客人吃泡在湯裡的麵糰嗎⋯⋯還以為連鎖店至少會有煮麵秒數的SOP，怎麼會連把麵煮熟都做不到？\",\"time\":1734611792,\"translated\":false},{\"author_name\":\"Daniel Lin\",\"author_url\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/110148454569549109813/reviews\",\"language\":\"zh-Hant\",\"profile_photo_url\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVGTOOjU712ZHQMY1aE6lporlvccQZnXbkojzkZbuwKwsNy9pEv-g=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba7\",\"rating\":4,\"relative_time_description\":\"1 年前\",\"text\":\"20240521,23 周年牛肉麵一碗99元，來吃了兩天。肉不少，湯也不錯。就是盛辣椒、酸菜的碟子上面有油漬像沒洗乾淨。\",\"time\":1716463563,\"translated\":false},{\"author_name\":\"Hsiu-Haung Lin\",\"author_url\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/106258726867058020542/reviews\",\"language\":\"zh-Hant\",\"profile_photo_url\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXojWQbqNP_xmWUrZDvjNh7zC0_7pLOdVhFhat-TQ6iqeisoeqT=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6\",\"rating\":2,\"relative_time_description\":\"1 年前\",\"text\":\"趁四十週年慶祝特價來吃牛肉麵。雖然價格親民，但是整體感受不是很好。首先牛肉麵的肉很硬很難咬，麵跟菜也就一般水平。唯一好的是湯，味道很棒。\\n人員服務上，剛好遇上一波客人比較多的狀況，但不知道為什麼前場除負責點餐的店員外，其他人都沒有在處理收餐盤與清潔。連到我餐點上來之後，前個客人的碗盤都還在桌上。\\n雖然最近週年慶會比較忙，可以理解。不過這樣水平，真的是吃附近的麵食館可能還比較好。\",\"time\":1702698433,\"translated\":false}],\"photos\":[\"AXQCQNRC6eeHEeM_S-R6lxIzfSJpnBDKv_eBKbhkbLPyivaCeR-8u2IvMpWqbJGtc2Vh-EfVSAq5PkWTM0xlEj2nhd7rc_6ooJTbnehVLXjwceC09fm-RyVUOd76blAoKT2RHbUgdPWlW3Y3s74KxCu3Ac9J9ImeD9QE3mPmlWdQUFNNLL-g_trPxUi5_jKT8yieW3M6msLjtEEXgZXtaflhQbOIpU6jIb9yjnXE5CjZauDonC5a_kUJ8AdkQXwfL0BvZ46J77xFAwO6ZyxQ05YRB1lzUpksYFW1wUgUu9ULIKXQamX3Y3LeUlZtPAHKCP9fKf_xDcKDR1f88s2PfdsjHMz2bpn0xLtPvmd8qVT_QSLoyKgZJpzi_Lqy7oxa9viChMKh5Vvwu6IY2ReCZTZf5lnIejQbYXW7e__SosohD3387ge_GRU-pYAxW_J-0oUYoVXslC8zO8wvV7RuAKmo_nn4XyKDb__WiRCXu_6S61efH5pI9MgcJQyKhMT_BqJbA3bjWvQf3xqkaftavpZnTgYEeozE51SdNckQX5UDndDb5SHkvaMSjsDh81sKUBz2PKInSP85dLktiEViWgDka8aWxEPdW_g6nESD9OvTTFWx5DYsoe7FhkkxR2QUBNBSwLFj1Y9z\",\"AXQCQNR64_CyfxIBJD6-znbWaNS4gUSMK4cWBLK7z1GUMJo81xE6TFt473sh1yWkT6WDe3IQVdeSycGz2rzcOtg8oiXDabgvxDYclud-S1fvrbB3lXECYZv4e9NHuD